  <!-- Start Update Input -->
  We ran into a slight problem last night, that 
being that there was nothing up for us to kill =\ 
Luckily, since we waxxed Sontalak the night 
before along with Eashen and Ikatiar, there was 
plenty of space for Myga farming!
<br>
<center><img src="http://www.furys-
edge.com/news/october18/sont.gif">
</center><br>
Thankfully we didnt have that same problem 
tonite, KT popped sometime during the day, so 
thats where we went! Id just like to thank Verant 
for the new resistance changes, its possibly the 
most fun they've allowed necros to have in almost 
3 years.
<br><center>
<img src="http://www.furys-
edge.com/news/october18/kt.gif">
</center><br>
Rather than calling it early after KT we just ran 
up the ramp and nailed these two buggers. Hey, 
they're up, why not? We got our first earring 
from Vindicator finally. Not sure if its the 
first on the server or not, we havent killed 
Derakor in...months?
<br><center>
<img src="http://www.furys-
edge.com/news/items/livingthunderearring.jpg">
</center><br>
Statue dropped 2 cloaks of Totalownage, 1 reaver 
of Gratsmort, and 90% of the raid force! We also 
found out that its alot more fun to fight SoRZ 
after several pulls when buffs are dropping and 
clerics are oom. Its ok though, our intense 
positioning efforts won the fight for us.
<br><center>
<img src="http://www.furys-
edge.com/news/october18/sorz.gif"></center>
